      <title>几乎智利所有人都希望加强移民限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/chile-overwhelmingly-scorns-immigration-poll-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项最新民意调查显示，由于新移民的涌入颠覆了该地区最富裕经济体之一的政治局面，智利民众要求实施更严格的移民管制的呼声远远高于其他拉丁美洲国家的邻国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/chile-overwhelmingly-scorns-immigration-poll-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
